Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.60,0:00:20.12,OP English,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}I walked ten thousand miles,ten thousands miles to see you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:27.00,OP English,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}And ever gasp to breath,I grabbed it just to find you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:33.82,OP English,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}I climbed up every hill to get to you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:40.65,OP English,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}I wandered ancient lands to hold just you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.91,0:00:48.76,OP English,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}And every single step of the way,I paid
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:01:00.79,OP English,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Every single night and day I searched for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.03,0:01:12.52,OP English,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Through sand storms and hazy dawns I reached for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.60,0:00:20.12,OP Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}我步行萬里  一萬里只為見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:27.00,OP Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}從不向瞬間喘息  緊扼住每一絲遇見的契機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:33.82,OP Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}我攀上每一座丘陵  尋找那邂逅的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:40.65,OP Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}徘徊於遠古的大陸  而我想佔據的  僅僅是你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.91,0:00:48.76,OP Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}一路上留下的每一個腳印  是我付出的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:01:00.79,OP Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}每一個孤單的黑夜白天裡  我尋找著你
