Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.30,0:01:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面就是橋了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這橋的氣氛不錯嘛  我說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好走過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  還撐得住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:47.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流了一身冷汗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是住在這附近的人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座橋已經支撐不住了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去的時候也還要過去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.90,0:03:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要在這裡停留多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我自己也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識寄這封信的人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路途遙遠辛苦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:34.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  這邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的女兒花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大約三年前  她從那個藤橋上掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然活了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:47.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但之後就一直那個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會向著太陽的方向發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也找了很多醫生看過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有發現頭上有被撞過的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然不知道為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你還在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  花怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  你們原來很要好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我把花變成那個樣子的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了！請你一定要救她！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能帶我去那個谷底一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  告訴我花掉下山谷時候的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  我說  別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我已經躲不開了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是本家來提親的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果拒絕的話  給這個村子的資助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會停止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不能拒絕…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.90,0:05:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這麼做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人全部都會被村裡處以私刑的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.90,0:05:34.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父母是理解我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父母如果真心希望你得到幸福的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一定能夠忍耐的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果留下來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無法按照自己的願望生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們離開這個山谷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻過山去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到寬廣明亮的土地上去生活吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起走吧！花！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點！那裡有一點脆了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣只有我們逃走  是不會幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會忍受的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善你會一直想著我吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會一直思念著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算到了那邊  心會壓抑而死  我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:47.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  先過橋去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:10.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來掉到那麼深的谷底是根本沒有希望活下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花卻自己走回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  身體已經變成一個空殼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:08:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都嘆息說她成了「谷底回還者」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「谷底回還者」？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個山谷裡有時會出現這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉到谷底去  雖然活著回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是心卻像是被什麼吃掉了似的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說如果谷中架起「一夜橋」的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們就會死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也就是傳聞罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「一夜橋」？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:29.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人見過在谷中只存在了一個晚上的橋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過已經是很久以前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像確實有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和現在附在花身上的是同一種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花被…附身了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一種被稱作「偽葛」的藤蔓狀蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都沒有看到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就是很難看得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.10,0:09:19.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這偽葛很脆弱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是從反方向拉的話就很結實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和文獻上看到的完全一樣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽光已經照不到這裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集到殘留下的陽光中了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡太缺乏陽光的照射了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:09:59.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  知道什麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於你來說是個殘酷的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「谷底回還者」和「一夜橋」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕都不是什麼傳聞而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都可以用偽葛來解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然平常偽葛是寄生在樹上的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個山谷中的偽葛卻會寄生在…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄生在生物的體內而逃離谷底吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們需要更多的日光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是自己卻沒有爬上山谷的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是就會附在動物身上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照射陽光  聚集力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的偽葛到達一定數量之後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會從宿主身上出來  結成群落跨過山谷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遷移到更加適合生存的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大概就是一夜橋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個山谷裡  大約每二十年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會發生一次「蟲的遷移」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  為什麼那個時候「谷底回還者」會死？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些蟲離開之後  不就應該恢復正常了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛我搜尋了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現這個谷底沒有動物的屍骨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偽葛寄生在屍體上的可能性很大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣的話  就算偽葛離開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只會變回屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  花也總有一天會…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是今年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次聽說有人看到了一夜橋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我爺爺出生的那一年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺今年六十歲了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能讓它延緩一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要求你把她救活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能讓她再多活一陣子就可以了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.15,0:12:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣維持下去才是讓她能活得最久的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.95,0:12:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能把這蟲驅除吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:38.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣做的話  十有八九她會當場身亡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為她這樣活下去對她來說是幸福的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不如…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不做這種無謂的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.55,0:12:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果三年前那個時候她還活著的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.35,0:13:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夜橋出現之後  就會平安恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西會不會出現還不知道呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果花現在恢復的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一樁好婚事等著她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不能讓人家再等下去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能接受你的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然她已經不能被稱之為「她」了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即使如此也還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能當做物品來對待
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.55,0:13:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀古先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:39.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  善
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這就要走了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這麼打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算明天去把橋修理一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我家裡去住一晚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:13:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己一個人住在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.05,0:13:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然家人住在村裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是所謂被「處以私刑」流放出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和村裡人完全分離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有想過要一個人離開這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  雖然想過很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是花還活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果花不在了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕很快就會離開了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於還是掉下去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:14:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因為你過了這橋啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人也不會走這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.95,0:15:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  快點再重新建一座啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.45,0:15:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.95,0:15:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這個時節大家都很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕會比較花時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把那位蟲師藏在這裡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有話要和他說啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.35,0:15:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它也是「谷地回還者」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許這裡還有更多的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.85,0:16:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會在這裡？你要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:31.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.25,0:16:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還活著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是花吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是失去了記憶吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底對她做了什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過不要再接近花了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:17.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼吸停止了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花  振作點  花！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:43.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花…死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從腦袋裡…爬出一條黑線一樣的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.85,0:17:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.25,0:17:59.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善啊  你也趕快離開這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點離開比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也許今天晚上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.25,0:18:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會架起一夜橋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.85,0:18:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這邊應該可以過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡已經聚集了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積攢力量到連你都能看得見的偽葛了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了半夜時一定會出現的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果放過這個機會  什麼時候才能離開可就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎  沒有任何留戀了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座橋  想往回走就會掉下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  總會有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘掉她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定能夠忘記她的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要離開這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼？已經回不去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.15,0:19:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒辦法走下去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡面有一條曾經是花…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:19:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對！花在三年前就死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.65,0:20:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:08.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這三年間  是因為花還活著我才能撐過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.75,0:20:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然看著她那副樣子很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.05,0:20:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在更加確信了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.95,0:20:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踩著她…我做不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別往回走！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.55,0:20:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後  他究竟怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.85,0:21:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.95,0:21:08.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  恐怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那座山谷裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.85,0:21:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會架起一晚的橋再度出現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概又是在二十年之後了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.97,0:23:37.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,0)}籠之中


